version

public static java.lang.String version()
Retrieves the Link library version string. This API can be called at any time, after getting GnManager instance successfully. The returned string is a constant. Do not attempt to modify or delete.

Example: 1.2.3.123 (Major.Minor.Improvement.Build)
Major: New functionality
Minor: New or changed features
Improvement: Improvements and fixes
Build: Internal build number

buildDate

public static java.lang.String buildDate()
Retrieves Link library build date string.

Returns:
Note Build date string of the format: YYYY-MM-DD hh:mm UTC

Remarks:

This API can be called at any time, after getting GnManager instance successfully. The returned string is a constant. Do not attempt to modify or delete. Example build date string: 2008-02-12 00:41 UTC
